TI  - Tilapia grow-out culture manual for smallholder farmers in Myanmar.
T2  - Tilapia grow-out culture manual for smallholder farmers in Myanmar
M3  - Miscellaneous
AB  - The objective of this manual is to assist the genetically improved farmed tilapia (GIFT) grow-out farmers from the Myanmar delta region in applying tilapia grow-out production technologies. These technologies apply to grow-out production in ponds and Chan Myaung (garden canal for plantation, especially which are prevalent in delta and is alternatively utilized for fish farming). Topics include pond preparation, fertilization, stocking, grow-out farming, feed processing, feeding regimen, monitoring during grow-out, preparedness for natural disasters, harvesting, marketing, record keeping, dealing with potential diseases and building the management capacity of farmers to enhance their knowledge. This manual was developed based on results from on farm trials and fish farming activities implemented by WorldFish.
